<p>School didn't teach you to easily convert units of measurements from Sta=
ndard to Metric? Is there even an easy way to convert them?&nbsp; Yes, just=
 click on the link below for a handy conversion chart.</p>
<p>Have you ever been ready to purchase fabric for a pattern and only to fi=
nd various fabrics in different widths to choose from?&nbsp; The calculator=
 below will convert yardage based on fabric width.<img class=3D"" lazyload"=
"=3D"" src=3D"https://www.needlepointers.com/articleimages/15-Sewing-Calcul=
ators-Charts-Calculator-Tape-Measure.jpg" alt=3D"Sewing Calculators Charts =
- Calculator and Tape" height=3D"415" width=3D"600"></p>
